   1:../main.c     **** /******************************************************************************
   2:../main.c     ****  * @file     EasyMain.c
   3:../main.c     ****  * @brief    Uses a system timer to toggle the  ports P1.0, P1.1, with 200ms
   4:../main.c     ****  * 			 frequency. LEDs that are connected to these ports will toggle
   5:../main.c     ****  * 			 respectively.
   6:../main.c     ****  * 			 In addition it uses the UART of USIC Channel 0 to send a message
   7:../main.c     ****  * 			 every 2s to a terminal emulator. The communication settings are
   8:../main.c     ****  * 			 115.2kbps/8N1. P2.2 is configured as input (RXD) and P2.1 is
   9:../main.c     ****  * 			 configured as output(TXD).
  10:../main.c     ****  *			 This project runs without modifications on the XMC 2Go Kit (XMC1100)
  11:../main.c     ****  * @version  V1.3
  12:../main.c     ****  * @date     4. March 2016
  13:../main.c     ****  * @note
  14:../main.c     ****  * Copyright (C) 2014 Infineon Technologies AG. All rights reserved.
  15:../main.c     ****  ******************************************************************************
  16:../main.c     ****  * @par
  17:../main.c     ****  * Infineon Technologies AG (Infineon) is supplying this software for use with
  18:../main.c     ****  * Infineon’s microcontrollers.
  19:../main.c     ****  * This file can be freely distributed within development tools that are
  20:../main.c     ****  * supporting such microcontrollers.
  21:../main.c     ****  * @par
  22:../main.c     ****  * THIS SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED "AS IS".  NO WARRANTIES, WHETHER EXPRESS, IMPLIED
  23:../main.c     ****  * OR STATUTORY, INCLUDING, BUT NOT LIMITED TO, IMPLIED WARRANTIES OF
  24:../main.c     ****  * MERCHANTABILITY AND FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE APPLY TO THIS SOFTWARE.
  25:../main.c     ****  * INFINEON SHALL NOT, IN ANY CIRCUMSTANCES, BE LIABLE FOR SPECIAL, INCIDENTAL,
  26:../main.c     ****  * OR CONSEQUENTIAL DAMAGES, FOR ANY REASON WHATSOEVER.
  27:../main.c     ****  *****************************************************************************/
